name: square haze #39
description: Sometimes I feel that I stuck in the maze. Sometimes I feel that this is just another loop of the cycle that goes over and over. Like all of this happened before, all this aesthetics is repeat itself and I can't do anything new. But it is not: with each repetition this walls are weaken. This is another piece in series of 91 unique generative artworks minted in individual 1/1 NFTs. Made in p5js. Kitty generated with StyleGan2. 2048 x 2048, 02 May 2021 //NEURAL HAZE
